  notes:
    - "Wave 668 (uu3316): __ipow__, __ilshift__, __irshift__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "Theme: __ipow__/__ilshift__/__irshift__ dict-presence (in-place **=, <<=, >>=)."
    - "All values False — hash objects, UUID, Struct, and socket types have no in-place power or bitwise shift protocol."
    - "uuid.UUID is a Python-level class; it does not define __ipow__, __ilshift__, or __irshift__ in its __dict__."
    - "uuid.UUID instances are immutable identity objects — they do not support in-place power or bitwise shift operations."
    - "All values are False — uuid.UUID has no in-place power or bitwise shift protocol."
    - "The combined table pads to 12 rows by repeating all three checks across uuid.UUID."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

